                                                                        Monitoring Metrics

    Server metrics:
        •	CPU
            1.	CPU used
            2.	CPU load
            3.	CPU temperature
        •	Memory usage
        •	I/O
            1.	Disk space usage
            2.	IO read, IO write
        •	Network
            1.	Network traffic
            2.	TCP connection states
        •	Sever state (Running/Stopped)

    Application metrics:
        •	SSL certificates validate status
